data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Seller has accepted an offer!!!Back up offers are welcome!!! Built in 2018, this beautiful home has everything you need. As you walk in you will find beautiful hardwood and accent lighting throughout the home. This home features Stainless steel appliances, equipped with a home wine refrigerator and it is smart home equipped! Bedrooms are located on the second floor of the home for privacy and tranquility; Every room includes ceiling fan. The backyard has a beautiful patio with doghouse or playhouse. Hurricane shutters also included.  Located in Sereno community, a beautiful community loaded with amenities including a basketball court, resort style pool, dog park and more at a very low quarterly HOA fee. Internet service is also included at the moment.  Truly a great space to entertain your guest, don’t let this home pass you by!
